          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have built hundreds of presentations over the years. Hours spent dragging text boxes, fiddling with alignment, swapping colors at 2 AM. Then I found ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", and honestly, a huge part of that grunt work just vanished.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma is a web-native AI platform that turns a text prompt into polished presentations, documents, websites, social media posts, and even graphics — all in under a minute. No downloads. No templates you have to wrestle with. You describe what you want, and Gamma delivers a finished deck that actually looks professional.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is not another \"AI wrapper\" that spits out ugly slides. Gamma produces clean, modern, visually coherent content that holds its own against manually designed work. If you have ever dreaded starting a pitch deck from scratch, keep reading.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why Gamma Stands Out Among AI Presentation Tools",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "There are plenty of AI tools that promise to build slides for you. I have tested most of them. Here is why Gamma kept earning its spot on my browser tab:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Speed without sacrifice.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " I once typed \"investor pitch deck for a sustainable packaging startup\" into Gamma at 8:47 AM. By 8:48, I had 12 slides with relevant content, clean layouts, and iconography that made sense. Not placeholder nonsense — actual, usable structure.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "True web-native design.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Gamma does not just copy PowerPoint conventions. Its cards (Gamma calls slides \"cards\") feel like a modern web experience. You can embed videos, interactive elements, and even publish them as live websites. The output feels native to how people actually consume content in 2024.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Import and export flexibility.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Already have a PDF or PPTX you want to revamp? Gamma imports them and lets you rebuild with AI. Need to export? You can save to PDF, PPTX, PNG, or even push directly to Google Slides. No format lock-in.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Generous free tier.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " You get 400 credits at signup and can create up to 10 cards per prompt for free. That is enough to genuinely evaluate the tool before committing a dollar. Most competitors gate basic functionality behind a paywall — Gamma lets you experience the real thing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
