        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The AI output is not always perfect on the first pass. Sometimes the copy needs tightening. Sometimes a slide layout does not quite match what I envisioned. But the starting point is so far ahead of a blank canvas that editing feels like refining rather than creating from nothing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The web-native approach means I never worry about software updates, compatibility issues, or file versioning. Everything lives in the cloud, accessible from any browser.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "And the pace of improvement is remarkable. Features that did not exist three months ago — graphics generation, social media templates, enhanced API — are already live and working well. The team behind Gamma ships fast and listens to feedback.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
