    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/gamma.app as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A professional at a desk watching colorful presentation slides generate on screen with a cup of coffee nearby. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Gamma AI free to use?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Gamma offers a free plan that includes 400 credits at signup, up to 10 cards per prompt, and the ability to create presentations, documents, websites, social posts, and images. You can also import from PDF and PPTX and export to multiple formats — all without a credit card.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use Gamma to build a website?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Every Gamma project can be published as a live, responsive website with its own shareable URL. It is ideal for quick landing pages, portfolio sites, and event pages without needing any coding or a separate website builder.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does Gamma compare to PowerPoint or Google Slides?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma takes a fundamentally different approach. Instead of manually building slides, you describe what you want in a text prompt and Gamma generates a complete, visually polished presentation in seconds. It also supports web-native features like embedded media and live publishing, which traditional slide tools do not offer.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What formats can I export from Gamma?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Gamma supports export to PDF, PPTX, PNG, and Google Slides. You can also share any project as a live web link. This flexibility means you are never locked into one format and can collaborate with teams that use different tools.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
